                <p>
                <app loc="1"><lem>τὀ̄πόλλō<unclear>ν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ος</supplied></lem>
                    <rdgGrp resp="#maffre2007"><rdg>τὀ̄πόλλō<unclear>ν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ος</supplied></rdg>
                    <rdg>τὀ̄πόλλō<unclear>ν</unclear><supplied reason="lost">ι</supplied></rdg></rdgGrp>
                    <rdg resp="#SECir">τὀπόλλ<supplied reason="lost">ōνι</supplied> <note>Oliverio</note></rdg></app></p>
            </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="fr" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Dîme d'Apollon.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Apollo's tithe.</p>
         </div><div type="translation" xml:lang="it" xml:space="preserve">
            <p>Decima di Apollo.</p>
         </div><div type="commentary">
                
                <p>With the nominative case <foreign xml:lang="grc">δεκάτα</foreign>, the god's name should have the genitive.</p>
